<h2 class="wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex">Sponsorship Opportunities</h2>
<p></p>
<p>Sponsoring FRC 5190: Green Hope Falcons can be beneficial not only for corporations but also for small businesses and start-ups. We love to see interest in our cause and believe it is our duty to help market groups who help us. To do this we have specific sponsorship levels that will help your company market itself based upon its endorsement of our robotics team. To receive information on sponsoring or donating to the Green Hope FRC Robotics team please contact us at one of our many sources and we will send you a sponsorship packet containing information about our team, reasons to sponsor us, and other useful information.</p>
<p></p>
<p>Email<a class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="e6d3d7dfd6858987858ea6818b878f8ac885898b" href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection">[email protected]</a></p>
<p></p>
<p>AddressAddress: 6905 Fayetteville Road, Suite 204 (Second Floor)</p>
<p></p>
<p>Hours of Operation:</p>
<p></p>
<p class="has-text-align-left">Weekdays – 6 P.M. – 8:30 P.M.</p>
<p></p>
<p class="has-text-align-left">Saturday – 10 A.M. – 4 P.M.</p>
<p></p>
<p class="has-text-align-left">Sunday – 12 P.M. – 4 P.M.</p>
<p></p>
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Support Levels</h2>
<p></p>
<p>We hope you will consider supporting our efforts to keep our team and STEM Education going strong.</p>
<p></p>
<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Golden Falcon ($5,000+)</h4>
<p></p>
<p>Receive the most prominent recognition on our robot, banners, t-shirts, website, and demonstration of our robot.</p>
<p></p>
<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Silver Falcon ($1,000)</h4>
<p></p>
<p>Receive recognition on our banners, t-shirts, website, and demonstration of our robot.</p>
<p></p>
<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Bronze Falcon ($500+)</h4>
<p></p>
<p>Receive the most prominent recognition on our t-shirts and website.</p>
<p></p>
<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Falcon (Up to $499)</h4>
<p></p>
<p>Receive recognition on our website and are welcome to attend all events.</p>
<p></p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Please Consider Donating</h3>
<p></p>
<p>Roboboosters, Inc.PO Box 5371Cary, NC 27512</p>
<p></p>
<p>Be sure to list FRC 5190 on the memo line of your check. Your donations are tax deductible. Some corporations have gift matching. We are a 501 (c)(3) non-profit. We are also happy to accept donations-in-kind.</p>
<p></p> 
